# Lisa Web — environment configuration example.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` (ignored by git) and edit the values.
# Vite only exposes variables prefixed with `VITE_` to the client bundle.

# Point Apollo at a real Lisa GraphQL server. When unset (default) the
# app runs against the in-memory `MockLink` so no backend is required.
# Example:
#   VITE_LISA_GRAPHQL_URL=https://lisa.example.com/Lisa/graphql
#VITE_LISA_GRAPHQL_URL=
